content: Hi - good question! <@1251730894046367785> Our text trainings have ended, but you can check out ⁠⁠<#1268426751164551199> to look through or ask about other texting opportunities. You can also go to https://go.kamalaharris.com/ to find more ways to get involved. We would love help with making phone calls during this final stretch -- you can sign up for that at https://events.democrats.org/event/725393/ . Thank you!

Thanks Nicole - I am already phone bank facilitating every day between now and the election, but we often find enthusiastic Harris supporters who are unable to phone bank, but are open to text banking. Since we need all hands on deck, I will point them to other text banking options. Thanks.
Ah apologies - misread your original thing that you are already phone bank captain (thank you!). Sounds good!
No worries. I know you are overseeing a big volume of messages! Thank you!!!!!
